Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.85,0:22:40.69,ED - R,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}omoi no atsusa ni mune ga kogareta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.86,0:22:47.99,ED - R,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}massugu ni shinken na kimi no hitomi
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.15,0:22:54.62,ED - R,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}onaji kurai no ai de kitto kitto kotaetai
